hackathon-description-text: Describe your hackathon and what makes it special. Many in-person hackathons include their event schedules here too.
hackathon-eligibility: Who can take part in your hackathon? List eligibility requirements such as age, citizenship, location, team size, or organization.
hackathon-requirements: Clearly tell hackers what they need to build for the hackathon and anything additional they should submit on Devpost.
hackathon-rules:
You should consult a lawyer before finalizing the rules for your hackathon. Here are some
